Name: JungleShoot
About the game: GamePlay: Hunt and kill as much militia soldiers as you can. How long can you stay alive? Features: • Guns: Find them in the jungle, your need lots of guns! • KillCount: Keeps track of all your kills • Jungle: A jungle filled with bad guys • HardCore: No save/load, no health bar. • Militia: Militia can only be killed temporarily. They will be back!
